  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Photograph</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1927</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The frameless still photograph features a dark car, a driver holding open the door and an elegantly dressed couple. The driver is wearing a greatcoat and cap. The man is dressed in a top hat, a dark three-piece suit with a white waistcoat, a white shirt and a white bow tie. The woman is wearing a dark gown, a cloak with a bud on it and has her hair cut in a bob.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Grešnica bez greha’ (Sinner without sin) is a silent feature film directed by Serbian filmmaker Kosta Novaković (1927).</ab>
